-Mm2HtWkN9U-swgjpd4X.text: Incident reported at 1806 Russell Ave N.

-Mm2Hu2v8yALsO9Mav9u.text: Firefighters have received an unconfirmed report of two vehicles on fire.

-Mm2Ii4lExVQSAJ_60BN.text: Firefighters are en route. Police are also responding to the vicinity for a ShotSpotter alert. Officers are unsure if the reported vehicle fire set off the alert. ShotSpotter technology is triggered by loud noises, including gunshots, fireworks, and backfiring vehicles.

-Mm2J57P6sJIHhV42nyx.text: Firefighters at the scene have confirmed the two vehicles on fire. An additional report from the police states that there is another vehicle on fire across the street.

-Mm2KdeO6IaGm_fe9HMf.text: Officers on the scene have confirmed that there are three vehicles on fire.
